line_items.name: LS 24" 4K All-In-One - Standard
line_items.description:
Technical Specifications:
Feature	Specification
Camera	4K SONY 1/2.8 CMOS Sensor
Pixel Density	8 million pixels
Optical Interface Options	F16, F18, F20, F22, F25, F28, F32
Display	24” Glass 4K monitor
Aspect Ratio	16:9
Resolution	2160p
Video Outputs	HDMI, DVI, and VGA output
Light Source	Integrated 80W LED rated for 70,000 hrs
Built-in Hard Disk	256GB
Local Playback	Yes
Voltage Range	100–240V
Included	- 24” Glass 4K Medical Monitor
	- Water-resistant 4K Sony CMOS Camera Head
	- Light Source Cable
	- 32 GB USB Drive
Weight	15.7kg (with base bracket)
Dimensions (CM)	59(L) x 42(W) x 8(H)

HD Version:
•	24" 4K Model (SKU: PLS24UHD1): 4K version for comprehensive diagnostics.
